# Purcari Israel - Project Overview

## About This Project
This is a Hebrew RTL ecommerce website for **Purcari Winery Israel** - a premium wine retailer selling Moldovan wines to Israeli customers.

## Key Facts
- **Language**: Hebrew (עברית) - RTL layout
- **Currency**: Israeli Shekel (₪)
- **Brand**: Purcari Winery (established 1827)
- **Target**: Premium wine consumers in Israel
- **Cart Rules**: Dynamic shipping, discounts, and restrictions managed via Appwrite.

## Tech Stack
- React 18.2 + TypeScript
- Vite 6 (build tool)
- Redux Toolkit 2.2.3 + RTK Query
- React Router DOM 6
- Framer Motion 12 (animations)
- Tailwind CSS (CDN)
- Lucide React (icons)

## Project Structure
```
├── components/     # Reusable UI components
├── pages/          # Route-level pages
